      "value": "<p>If you see this \"Error: Invalid API key\" message, it likely indicates that you are on an outdated version of the app.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Please look for an update in your app store for: Edge- Crypto &amp; Bitcoin Wallet, or click the appropriate download link from here: <a href=\"https://edge.app/get-started\">https://edge.app/get-started</a></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>With the latest version of the app installed, would you please let us know if issue still persists?</p>"
